    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<CostCenter>> OrganizationsItemCostCentersThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<CostCenter> costCenters = getCostCenterService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalCostCentersCount = costCenters.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<CostCenter> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<CostCenter>(costCenters, totalCostCentersCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
    }
    
